Title: Larva
Writer: Kenneth M. Badish, Boaz Davidson, David Goodin
Actors: Vincent Ventresca, Rachel Hunter, William Forsythe
Plot: In Host, Missouri, the newcomer vet, Dr Eli Rudkus, is called by a farmer to look at one of his cows. The vet finds a strange parasite in the animal and sends it to the agriculture lab to be looked into. He soon finds another one ...
